padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":28}},"product_tabs_tdKRVz":{"type":"product-tabs","blocks":{"row_TprFA4":{"type":"row","settings":{"tab_name":"Heritage","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Fjords_History.webp","caption":"","heading":"Fjords Legacy","text":"<p>The journey began in 1941, when brothers Otto and Mindor Hjellegjerde started producing furniture in the cellar of their family home in Sykkylven, a picturesque fjord village in Møre and Romsdal, Norway. What started as a small-scale effort was fueled by determination and craftsmanship.<\/p><p>As demand steadily increased, the cellar workshop was expanded, and in 1946, their third brother, Ingvald, joined the venture. Together, they shared a vision of creating functional and beautifully designed furniture.<\/p><p>Over time, their passion and innovation transformed a humble family workshop into one of Norway’s largest furniture groups, influencing the evolution of the nation’s furniture industry.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"row_8MMq8Q":{"type":"row","disabled":true,"settings":{"tab_name":"Spring","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5_992eea99-cde9-46e7-ab51-54e49fb4443f.png","caption":"","heading":"Spring","text":"<p>This spring construction is designed to be both sturdy and comfortable. It features a combination of heavy-duty sinuous springs with each layer connected with elastic webbing to ensure durability and long-lasting comfort. This construction is designed to ensure maximum comfort, support, and durability.<\/p>","button_label":"Button label","button_link":""}},"row_MNjzWf":{"type":"row","disabled":true,"settings":{"tab_name":"Dubetina","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/COMFORT-hero_banner.png","poster_video_local":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/f3892e03121f4bd28528395930502ee9.mp4","caption":"","heading":"10mm Dubetina","text":"<p>Feathers collection have 10mm Dubetina, a soft and smooth cotton, providing extra layer of support. Its breathability and moisture wicking properties help to keep the sofa cool and dry. Additionally, the fabric is durable and designed to resist fading, pilling, and wear and tear.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"row_pXtCWw":{"type":"row","disabled":true,"settings":{"tab_name":"Foam","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cat-living2.png","caption":"","heading":"3 Layers of Foam","text":"<p>Pair text with an image to focus on your chosen product, collection, or blog post. Add details on availability, style, or even provide a review.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"row_9FHFGd":{"type":"row","disabled":true,"settings":{"tab_name":"Legs","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cat-dining2.png","caption":"","heading":"Leg Detail","text":"<p>This sleek silver painted leg finish will add a touch of modern sophistication to any living space. The legs are crafted from strong, durable wood and are finished with a high-gloss silver paint that is sure to withstand the test of time. The modern shape and sheen of the legs will give your sofa a unique and stylish feel.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["row_TprFA4","row_8MMq8Q","row_MNjzWf","row_pXtCWw","row_9FHFGd"],"settings":{"title":"Luxury from the inside out.","image_height":"medium","desktop_image_width":"medium","heading_size":"h1","text_style":"body","button_style":"secondary","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","image_layout":"align-left","section_color_scheme":"","row_color_scheme":"scheme-2","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"image_with_text_BaYQrx":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_8hGcjm":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Crafted for Comfort","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_WGnyPk":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Every Fjords product is a testament to craftsmanship, quality, and timeless Norwegian design. Sophisticated engineering blends seamlessly with elegant aesthetics, reflecting decades of expertise and innovation.<\/p><p>Each piece is the result o